es\", \"from\": 4462, \"to\": 4479}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This emphasis on repurposing and revitalizing existing facilities underscores the commitment to leave a lasting impact beyond the duration of the Games.\", \"from\": 4481, \"to\": 4633, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This emphasis\", \"from\": 4481, \"to\": 4494}, {\"ngram\": \"repurposing\", \"from\": 4498, \"to\": 4509}, {\"ngram\": \"existing facilities\", \"from\": 4527, \"to\": 4546}, {\"ngram\": \"the commitment\", \"from\": 4559, \"to\": 4573}, {\"ngram\": \"a lasting impact\", \"from\": 4583, \"to\": 4599}, {\"ngram\": \"the duration\", \"from\": 4607, \"to\": 4619}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 4623, \"to\": 4632}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Picture this: beach volleyball players engaging in thrilling matches right in front of the magnificent Eiffel Tower, while archery enthusiasts take aim at the historic Invalides monument.\", \"from\": 4635, \"to\": 4822, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4738, \"end\": 4750, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eiffel_Tower\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.086918085011487e-63, \"text\": \"Eiffel Tower\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eiffel_Tower\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eiffel_Tower\"}, {\"begin\": 4803, \"end\": 4812, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Les_Invalides\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.7785409195105032e-59, \"text\": \"Invalides\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Les_Invalides\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Les_Invalides\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Picture\", \"from\": 4635, \"to\": 4642}, {\"ngram\": \"beach volleyball players\", \"from\": 4649, \"to\": 4673}, {\"ngram\": \"thrilling matches\", \"from\": 4686, \"to\": 4703}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 4713, \"to\": 4718}, {\"ngram\": \"archery enthusiasts\", \"from\": 4758, \"to\": 4777}, {\"ngram\": \"aim\", \"from\": 4783, \"to\": 4786}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The vibrant atmosphere at Place de la Concorde becomes the backdrop for thrilling skateboarding competitions, and the Chateau de Versailles transforms into a grand stage for the equestrian events.\", \"from\": 4823, \"to\": 5019, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4849, \"end\": 4869, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.776448642906982e-31, \"text\": \"Place de la Concorde\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\"}, {\"begin\": 4941, \"end\": 4962, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palace_of_Versailles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chateau de Versailles\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palace_of_Versailles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palace_of_Versailles\"}, {\"begin\": 5001, \"end\": 5011, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 7.457625094754773e-12, \"text\": \"equestrian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The vibrant atmosphere\", \"from\": 4823, \"to\": 4845}, {\"ngram\": \"the backdrop\", \"from\": 4878, \"to\": 4890}, {\"ngram\": \"skateboarding competitions\", \"from\": 4905, \"to\": 4931}, {\"ngram\": \"a grand stage\", \"from\": 4979, \"to\": 4992}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These temporary venues have been carefully chosen to bring the excitement of the Games to iconic locations and to engage a wider audience.\", \"from\": 5021, \"to\": 5159, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These temporary venues\", \"from\": 5021, \"to\": 5043}, {\"ngram\": \"the excitement\", \"from\": 5080, \"to\": 5094}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 5098, \"to\": 5107}, {\"ngram\": \"iconic locations\", \"from\": 5111, \"to\": 5127}, {\"ngram\": \"a wider audience\", \"from\": 5142, \"to\": 5158}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not only do these choices minimize the environmental impact compared to constructing new facilities, but they also adhere to eco-design principles.\", \"from\": 5160, \"to\": 5307, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these choices\", \"from\": 5172, \"to\": 5185}, {\"ngram\": \"the environmental impact\", \"from\": 5195, \"to\": 5219}, {\"ngram\": \"new facilities\", \"from\": 5245, \"to\": 5259}, {\"ngram\": \"eco-design principles\", \"from\": 5285, \"to\": 5306}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The venues will be outfitted using reused or low-carbon materials, incorporating thoughtful landscaping, and embracing natural ventilation, all in an effort to create sustainable and environmentally friendly spaces.\", \"from\": 5308, \"to\": 5523, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The venues\", \"from\": 5308, \"to\": 5318}, {\"ngram\": \"reused or low-carbon materials\", \"from\": 5343, \"to\": 5373}, {\"ngram\": \"thoughtful landscaping\", \"from\": 5389, \"to\": 5411}, {\"ngram\": \"natural ventilation\", \"from\": 5427, \"to\": 5446}, {\"ngram\": \"an effort\", \"from\": 5455, \"to\": 5464}, {\"ngram\": \"sustainable and environmentally friendly spaces\", \"from\": 5475, \"to\": 5522}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A French puma helicopter lands during an exercise called \\\"Heracles\\\" focused on chemical, radiological and biological risks, ahead of the 2024 Olympic Games to be held in Paris, France, May 4, 2023.\", \"from\": 5525, \"to\": 5722, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5527, \"end\": 5533, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.8047374755558817, \"rank\": 0.23746015230075404, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 5695, \"end\": 5700, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.762261943089587e-2